THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE LICENSES

This software uses the following third-party components:

1. FFmpeg (https://ffmpeg.org/)
   License: LGPL 2.1+ or GPL 2+ (depending on build configuration)
   Used for: Video encoding, decoding, and capture

2. VapourSynth (https://www.vapoursynth.com/)
   License: LGPL 2.1
   Used for: Video processing and filtering framework

3. PyTorch (https://pytorch.org/)
   License: BSD 3-Clause
   Used for: AI model inference

4. PySide6 (https://doc.qt.io/qtforpython/)
   License: LGPL 3.0
   Used for: Graphical user interface

5. QTGMC (http://avisynth.nl/index.php/QTGMC)
   License: GPL 2.0
   Used for: Motion-adaptive deinterlacing

6. BM3D (https://github.com/HomeOfVapourSynthEvolution/VapourSynth-BM3D)
   License: GPL 3.0
   Used for: Video denoising

